content.detailedDescription: Driving south past hatch, nm, i saw the black object in the day time sky. i continued to monitor it as we drove and eventually took i-10 west bound and the entire time i was going through what it could possibly be.  would a helicopter hover hundreds of feet for approximately an hour?  i don't know much about helicopters so i don't know.  could it be a weather balloon?  maybe, but it seemed extremely large and completely black.  i am so very curious about what it could be and i felt a frustration at not being able to identify it.  we stopped to get gasoline after driving on i-10wb for about 15 minutes and when we came out of the gas station 10 minutes later, it was gone.
content.summary: Black blob like object was stationary in air for about an hour.

content.detailedDescription: While driving home tuesday night i observed a very bright white light in the sky. i am always on the lookout for lights due to childhood experiences. the light appeared to be in our atmosphere and had a blue tinge on one edge, i thought it was a plane. when i was almost home i realized that the light was not moving and there was a smaller different color light next to it, flashing red and green. i hurried down my driveway and stopped the car, grabbed my cell and walked behind another vehicle where i could observe the light better. i called my grandmother in the house and told her to send my son outside to look and turn off the porch light. my son came outside and grandma was soon to follow. i recorded the light for about 40 seconds on my phone. i was excited about this because it could not be an airplane and we had been hearing other reports of ufos in the area, being seen by family and friends. i have had many experiences in my past and have not seen much activity for a long while. i regret now not recording longer, i just wasn't sure what i was seeing. i needed to go inside and make dinner, etc. so grandma and i left my son outside to watch. he came in saying that after we left, he had witnessed the smaller light wavering back and forth really rapidly. we finished dinner and i finally settled down for the evening. i remembered that i had not looked at the footage yet and when i watched the clip i couldn't believe it! the white light was not a white light! it looked like a row of windows and then i emailed myself the video. i was thinking this is crazy, could i finally have proof that i am not delusional and that everyone who has doubted and laughed me will see that i am telling the truth? i pulled up the video on my computer and put it on powerpoint so that i could magnify it and run it slowly. it took a few views before i decided to put it on the tv. when watching on the larger screen my grandmother and i discovered that at about 36 -37 seconds there are two lights emitted from the object going to the right very quickly you could miss is it if you are not watching carefully and closely. they are red then white. i hope and pray this is the proof i need to show that what has happened to me is no laughing matter and that i am telling the truth. please analyze this! i am also submitting a daytime photo so that you can see where we observed the objects through the trees looking out over the ocean.
content.summary: Hovering lights over ocean

content.detailedDescription:
My children (two age 7) and i observed several "scrapes" in the sky.  that is short, bright white lines extending a short distance upward high in the sky. if left by jet aircraft earlier they would dissipate but these remained unchanged and were bright white for the several minutes that we observed them. as we moved along the highway (going south on nj turnpike) approaching them we only noticed a slight change,indicating they were high and not very close. when we exited the turnpike at exit 4, and changed direction, we lost sight of them due to buildings in the way.
please note this phenomena is different than anything i have seen when watching ufos on youtube. there was no apparent movement and no real object, just bright white lines unlike anything i have ever seen before.
we were left with the feeling we saw something special but as open as i am to seeing ufos, i cannot say we did due to the lack of movement and no observable objects.
content.summary: Several scrapes were noted in the southern sky

content.detailedDescription: I was driving to our local waste center when i looked up into the sky and saw this weird hole in the clouds it was what looked like a perfect circle, i got out of my car and took a picture of it with my iphone. i have been a pilot for over 35 years and had never seen anything like it before. i did not see the two black objects below the cloud formation until i got home and enlarged the picture on my computer. i downloaded the picture to the weather channel thinking some expert would comment on it and when i went back to check a few days later they had removed the picture from their site.

content.detailedDescription:
While driving around the country side(looking for unique winter scenes to photograph), north of bloomington / normal, il., and just west / north west of hudson, il, i stopped to capture a farm setting that had a large windmill towering above the property.  it was bitter cold and windy, so i took a number of exposures to make sure that i had a good frame without camera shake.  i was hand holding a canon mark iv with an 70-200mm f2.8 lens, at an iso of 125 for fine detail.

when i later processed and finalized copies of the raw images in dxo and photoshop, i was removing dust particles from the sky(that are placed there by the cameras image sensor at the time of shooting), when i spotted a bell / diamond shaped object just left of the windmill tower, and under the left fan blade that i have marked with (3) small arrow heads.  when the image is enlarged to 200 to 500%, the object has pretty good resolution, and has the appearance of a stubby, vertically sectioned / stepped object unlike a smooth weather balloons exterior.  at the location where the image was taken, i do not know of any weather stations in the surrounding area which is fairly remote, and i was shooting in a different direction from any large city.  it was to cold and windy for a pleasure craft such as a hot air balloon to be flying.  

after spotting the object in photoshop, i looked at all of my other frames taken within seconds or minutes of the one attached, and no others before or after have the object within the frame area.  i shoot everything in raw format, and i retain unprocessed raw files copies for future reference.

it is unfortunate that i did not see the object while shooting, or i could have captured it up to 800mm rather than 70mm.

exposure information;  1/320 sec. f10, 125 iso, 70mm.
content.summary: Bell/diamond shaped object, that does not appear to be smooth like a weather balloon.

content.detailedDescription: We were camped in the cascade mountains in a remote wilderness area.  at approximately 0300 we heard a strong humming swishing noise approaching us from above the trees, as it drew closer to us we drew our weapons ready to engage what ever it was.  after drawing our weapons the object did not approach us any closer then moved away.  it sounded like it stopped approximately 100 ft from our location.  there were no lights observed. after daylight at approximately 0800 two fighter jets flew by near where we heard the noises as if looking for something??  we are former military and often travel into remote wilderness areas but have never experienced a similar encounter previously.  however in speaking with local residents they have witnessed similar sounds and strange lights in the area we were at.
content.summary: Remote wilderness moved towards us above trees total darkness we drew weapons then it changed direction

content.detailedDescription: I was playing with my canon rebel t3i, taking pictures down my street and had a long exposure turned on (just under 30 seconds) to capture lighting. i didn't see these lights by eye, but after opening the photos, we noticed these green orb with detached disc patterns that seemed to be on a perfect circular axis. the object was not moving in a circle and constantly lit, otherwise, it would have showed up as a line of light like a plane does. about an hour afterward, i went back out to see if the same thing would occur. i took 4 photos a few minutes apart and there was no obvious lighting to the eye. the first showed nothing out of the ordinary, the second had a line of lights that at first i thought could somehow be reflections of some sort, the last ones had the same, but with a couple of lights "turned off". these weren't reflections, as far as i can tell, but also weren't stars, and were completely stationary. these were also shot on a long-exposure. if anyone can tell me what these are, i'd be much obliged! i will take more this evening to see if there is any consistency.
content.summary: Green lights caught by camera in circular pattern, followed by white lights in line

content.detailedDescription:
I am using my nightvision regularly during the nights in arosa, switzerland to watch the sky. i just let the videorecorder run and check in the morning the footage. usually i see a lot of airplanes but sometimes also round flying lights which might be satellites but they have various speed and on this video you can see two blinking stationary lights. this short video is the result of 15 hours video recording during the 5. and 7. january 2015 in arosa, switzerland. unfortunately my nightvision can only cover a small part of the sky and it would be helpful to watch and record the nightsky in a more structured manner because these walking and blinkings lights can be observed during every night. 
you will first see two flying lights, then an airplane for comparison reason and then two blinking stationary lights.
content.summary: First two ights unknown, third light is an airplane for comparison reason, last two lights are stationary.

content.detailedDescription:
I was reading in my living room and saw a light in the sky through the window that resembled a star, where i'd never witnessed a star before. i noticed it was sometimes lit up white, sometimes blue. it began skipping back and forth around a small area of the sky. then, it would hover for awhile. it would also completely disappear for a few seconds then reappear. sometimes the hovering was still, sometimes it seemed to be wavering. after about ten minutes, the object shot off at a high speed to the left (towards the north). i should note that this is close to an airport, but i know with all of my being that this was no kind of typical aircraft. it was also disturbing because the whole time i felt an extreme fear. as irrational as it seems, when it took off so quickly, i felt sure that it flew away because "they" had realized that i was watching, and i felt terrified that they were going to do something to harm me. 

i did try to get photos and video, but i was unable to pick up the object on my camera phone in the dark.
content.summary: Blue and white light hovered, blinked, skipped around, disappeared and reappeared, then shot off at a high speed to the left.

content.detailedDescription: Looked out patio door at 2 a.M., noticed some really bright solid green lights in the sky coming from the north airport area towards me. they were so round and bright! wondered what the heck was in the sky. so i sat there looking out door. when it got close to my house i could see at least 3 really large and bright green lights in the front, it could have had more green lights, i did not count. it was close to tree top level, i could hear thru my glass door it was really a loud noise it made, sounded like a really loud lawnmower in the sky. as it got close to house it turned to the east and i could see a bright flashing red light at back of this thing. i live near airport and see lights all the time on airplanes and helicopters. never heard one that sounded like this or seen anything that had that many large green lights on the front of it. it continued on going to the southeast of me. really strange! those bright green lights is what caused me to watch it. don't think it was an airplane, maybe some new kind of craft or helicopter?
content.summary: Bright green lights in front, red light in back sounded like lawnmower

content.detailedDescription: November 15th 2014 at approximately 5:25pm in columbia county south of arlington wisconsin on county i. while driving home from picking up my fiance from work i spotted one large orb of light that at first i mistook as a star, until it split in two i was shocked. one orb of light stayed stationary. the second half began to move east with lights moving counter clockwise. to my amazement it disappeared, only to reappear closer the first orb and continued with the same motion before both disappeared and did not appear again. after we got home, we had some time to realize what we saw, each detail has not left my mind since and i cant seem to forget it.
content.flightPath: Hovering then path,Straight-line path,Path then hovering
content.summary: Driving home from picking up my fiance from work i spotted one large orb of light that at first i mistook as a star, until it split in two. one orb of light stayed stationary. the second half began to move east with lights moving counter clockwise.

content.detailedDescription:
I was with my girlfriend on the beach at fire island ny watching the perseids meteor shower in august of 1972. a large object appeared over the ocean. we first thought it was just a large meteor. but it hovered above the ocean and changed direction. it settled into the ocean approximately 1/2 mile from us. we could see it shining under the water. it traveled quickly through the ocean towards our location. i had never seen anything like it before or since. there was a jetty and a small light beacon that i climbed on to get a better look. the object was coming quickly. the next thing we both knew was that it was almost 3am. over 4 hours passed without any sensation of time passing. both myself and my girlfriend were shaking and had an incredible sensation of fear. neither of us could remember what happened during the lost period of time. i will also add that neither myself or my girlfriend ever used drugs or alcohol. we were both sober and wide awake at the time of the event. my girlfriend was never the same after that. she withdrew from the world and never wanted me to see her again or to ever remind her of that night. as for myself. i have had a severe sleep disorder my entire life since that night. i have the same nightmare that i am being chased several nights a week for over 40 years.
i never get to see what or who is chasing me and i never know why i am being chased.
   this is a fact. i am not crazy or a liar. i have told this story to many of my friends most of my life. i did not make it up, and i have been laughed at most of my life because i told people about this event. i have actually talked to someone else that swears that he had the same missing time happen to him. that made me wonder if this happens often, that most people that lost time  never remember what happened. i am willing to answer any questions that you might ask. i have always wondered what happened to us. i have never been able to forget it. the memory stays as fresh as if it happened yesterday.
content.summary: Landed in ocean then quickly traveled to shore

content.detailedDescription:
1. my partner and i were researching online, we were facing an east side window overlooking the chicago loop skyline.

2. i glanced up from the computer screen and noticed the brightest light in the skyline.  i have lived in the same condo for 10+ years and have never seen this light before.  it was a bright white light and appeared to be shining directly into the condo.  i immediately asked my partner if he saw the light. 

3. i thought there must be a repair crew atop the building 1 block south of the huron consulting group building with a strange bright light directed in our direction.

4.  the object just hovered at the top of the building for roughly 5 seconds, it was dark outside and we could only tell that it was at the height of the top of the building, but then it began to descend in front of the building.  the top two floors of the building are windowless mechanical floors that are washed in white light, the ball of light descended to the top floor of windowed office space and then for a split second there was a 1/10th the white light's size ball of red light and then it disappeared...It did not appear to move away; it just disappeared. 

6. i can see 7 floors of the building below where it disappeared; it did not descend below another building; it just disappeared.  we turned off the condo's interior lights and continued watching the area for 15 mins + with binoculars and did not see anything; there were no people atop the building and no visible activity outside the building.  a helicopter hovered to the south and eventually circled around the loop with bright ( much less bright ) lights shining down.  also two planes flew in he distance, far south east.
content.flightPath: Stationary,Hovering then path,Path with directional change
content.summary: Brightest light in the sky (white), appeared to rest on the building 1 block south of the huron consulting grp., then it decended 50' in front of the bldg and vanished with a single red dot as it vanished

content.detailedDescription:
My family and i were on holiday in the kanali hotel apartments in sidari, corfu, greece. at between 1800hrs and 1810hrs i observed a disc like object hovering with  bit of a wobble. i was standing on the balcony of our apartment on the third floor looking northeast toward albania, the mountains of which could easily be seen. the sun was reflecting off the craft which drew my attention. it was approximately a mile away at an angle of about 50° above the surface of the sea.  
the craft itself was disc shaped like two plates on top of one another with one inverted. however in between the two plates was a section divided into squares which would go around the circumference on the craft.  each square was then divided by two diagonal lines. i was entranced by the object being mad on aircraft since a boy. i knew it was exotic.
my wife was next to me talking to our neighbours a man, a lady and their teenage daughter. i wanted to get a better look and went to get my binoculars rather than drawing anyone's attention to it.  no one else mentioned it, i told the wife who looked who just my wife is a counsellor and can be very diplomatic.
later that evening while reading in bed late at night on my kindle, i was facing the double patio doors which our bed faced.  there was the sound of the door sliding open which was weird because it was the opposite side to where the handle was.  the curtain was then grabbed by very skinny arm with elongated fingers each with a short pointed fingernail at the end.  a head then appeared looking right at me with huge almond shaped eyes which were black with no eyelids, almost no nose and a slit for a mouth. the colour was grey\brown and couldn't of been more than 4ft tall. it was a typical grey alien.
i was freaked!  paralysed with fear as you can imagine.  eventually after some time i got the courage to look out the patio door.  nothing was out there and nothing unusual could be seen in the sky.  i went back to bed and eventually fell asleep.  in the morning i discussed this with the wife, who said i was probably dreaming, it was my birthday i had been drinking, one pint of local larger and one shot of 3star metaxa brandy. it is possible that it reacted with my diabetic medication.
i've only told a few close friends and family. feeling i might be ridiculed.  i know my aircraft being a bit of a nerd and know it wasn't a mid identification.  a few weeks ago some kids had a drone in the local park with lights on and this event came to mind so i decided to report it.
content.summary: On hold in corfu, my birthday, after early dinner observed a disc object silver reflecting sun object was like two plates with a checkerboard pattern in the middle section between plates.

content.detailedDescription: My partner and i had just been to the coastal town of blythe near newcastle upon tyne.We were on our way home heading south along the coastal route on blythe road which runs through seaton sluice and takes you toward whitley bay links.It was a beautiful bright and clear sunny day the time was around 1.30 in the afternoon.  as we drove toward whitley bay links my partner suddenly said ,have you seen how low that aeroplane is coming over?As i looked i noticed that the aeroplane was not moving.She said its bloody low isn't it but didnt seem to notice that it wasn't moving which i couldn't understand. i said i can't believe it but it is the same aeroplane i had seen a month earlier with my father at exactly the same location.That event left me totally bewildered and wandering what had i witnessed.  i mentioned to my partner again it is not moving and this time i am going to pull over and stop for a better look.  i slowed down to practically a stand still when suddenly behind me out of nowhere a car was right behind us flashing it's headlights to be past us. i can't remember the car actually overtaking us or where it went from that moment.This is strange as the road is straight but bends to the left at the bottom taking you around toward whitley bay light house past the caravan park.  the aeroplane came from our right which is west and followed a straight path alternately stopping and moving on as we approached.The aeroplane moved at roughly walking pace passing over whitley bay cemetery and heading toward the light house.We came toward the bend and the aeroplane was right there in front of us bright blue and white lights flashing in sequence along the full length of both wings.As the aeroplane headed toward the light house it had practically came to a stand still in front of us.The plane looked like it was going to land in a near by field and came right down to practically ground level with lights still flashing out at sea toward the light house.I was in complete awe of what i was seeing as i was saying to my partner this is impossible for any kind of passenger aeroplane to do as we watched it hover at ground level.The aeroplane seemed to be signalling to something but i could not see anything around and then i thought to myself this is strange as there isn't anything around.I couldn't believe that no one else had seen this happening and that we were the only two people witnessing this event.  as we neared the plane toward the light house it seemed as though it new it was being observed and moved slowly off and stopping keeping ahead of us as we tried to get closer.  i remember looking and seeing what appeared to be a heat haze from the rear of the plane as it started to rise from ground level also i recall the plane seemed to have become a smaller version of what we had first witnessed a full sized thompson air craft with all the same colours. we reached the right hand bend running along whitley bay links and had to continue driving as the craft looked to be ready to move off toward the light house.There was no sound or roar of any engines nor any sign of any landing gear and any increase in speed.My partner does not recall the event as the way i seen it for myself and has a totally different recollection to me.We had our differences of what we had just seen  for the rest of our journey home.From the beginning of the sighting to the end seemed to last for 10 to 15mins all in slow motion i continue to question what we both saw on that day and have not yet got any answers for this account.
content.summary: Driving home from day out in blythe coastal town.Partner sighted low flying aircraft ahead which stopped motionless in air then moved off slowly as we followed it.

content.detailedDescription: I had just come back from using bathroom around 5am and laid down in bed and looked out the window because i always look at the skies and i saw a longish object with 3 bright lights one behind the other through the window. it hovered for about 10-15 minutes disappearing from view and reappearing before disappearing entirely. there was no street lights near it to be confused with and houses can't float so it wasn't house lights. when i realised it wasn't a street light i got out of bed and went to the window to take a better look . i was pretty sure of what it was right away. because i was a house guest i laid back down in bed quietly and tried to keep watching it but it disappeared and i went back to sleep. i only wish i had video of it. sorry. this is not the first time i have seen something like this.

content.detailedDescription: It was forth of july and i was with my girlfriend. we watched a firework show went back to her parents friends house and he sat on lawn chairs out back and were looking at the stars. i then see a glowing word which looked like a star. it began to move extremely fast up down and side to side. i told my girlfriend to get her dad he came and said it must be a satellite. i know it couldn't have been because it was moving in directions that could not have been a satellite and was moving across the sky extremely fast. then it bolted and was gone.
content.summary: It looked like a star but moved in many directions moving extremely fast
